## Use Case 10: Tính Estimated Tax Payment

**Khi nào dùng:** Trước các deadline Q1 (4/15), Q2 (6/15), Q3 (9/15), Q4 (1/15 năm sau)

**Prompt mẫu:**
```
Tính {{COMPUTED:CURRENT_QUARTER}} {{FISCAL_YEAR.YEAR}} Estimated Tax Payment.
Data:
- YTD revenue: $850,000
- YTD expenses: $620,000
- YTD taxable income: $230,000
{{IF:COMPANY.ENTITY_TYPE == "C-Corp"}}
- Federal corporate tax rate: 21%
- Prior year safe harbor: 100% of FY{{COMPUTED:PRIOR_FY}} tax
{{ENDIF}}
{{IF:COMPANY.ENTITY_TYPE IN ["S-Corp", "LLC-multi", "Partnership", "LLC-single", "Sole-Prop"]}}
- Pass-through entity: tax flows to owner's 1040-ES
- Owner's marginal rate (estimated): TBD
- Self-employment tax: 15.3% (if applicable)
{{ENDIF}}

Tính:
1. Current year method
2. Safe harbor method
3. Recommend phương án tối ưu
```

**Deliverable:**
- Calculation worksheet
- Recommended payment amount
- Form 1040-ES draft (pass-through) hoặc 1120-W (C-Corp)
- Reminder set cho next quarterly deadline

